  <!-- GENERATION SPLIT -->
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px">
    <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid #440000;border-radius:12px;padding:20px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;color:#CC0000;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px">⛽ GAS GEN — 2021–2023 (& 2024/25 CPO)</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7">Platform: Macan J1 (same since 2014, heavily updated 2019/2022)<br>Engine: 2.0T 4-cyl (261hp) or 2.9T V6 TT (375hp–434hp)<br>AWD: Porsche Traction Mgmt (permanent AWD)<br>Trans: 7-speed PDK<br>0-60: 5.8s (base) → 4.3s (GTS)<br>Fuel economy: ~11.5L/100km combined<br><span style="color:#4ade80">✓ Under $70k options exist · CPO available</span></div>
