    <div style="background:var(--surface);border-radius:12px;padding:20px">
      <h3 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px">🧾 Boxster Ownership Notes for Ottawa</h3>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:12px">
        <div style="background:var(--surface2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px">
          <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#4ade80;margin-bottom:4px">✅ Summer/Fall Experience</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)">Ottawa has genuinely beautiful driving roads — Gatineau Park, Champlain Bridge, Highway 50. A Boxster here May–October is incredible. The soft-top folds in 9 seconds at speeds up to 50km/h.</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--surface2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px">
          <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#f87171;margin-bottom:4px">❌ Winter Storage</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)">RWD + convertible = winter storage mandatory. Budget $150–$300/mo for indoor heated storage (Oct–Apr). Or: separate winter car (Civic, RAV4) + Boxster seasonally.</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--surface2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px">
          <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b;margin-bottom:4px">⚠️ IMS / Intermediate Shaft</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)">2017+ 718 uses a 4-cyl engine — IMS bearing issues of older 981 don't apply. Reliability is good. Main concern: coolant temp sensor, PCV, and convertible top hydraulics on high-km cars.</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--surface2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px">
          <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#60a5fa;margin-bottom:4px">💡 Manual vs PDK</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)">Manual is rarer (and better for driving fun). PDK is faster in lap times. The 2020 Orléans listing is manual — that alone makes it special. Manual Porsches hold value better at resale.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /porsche-boxster -->

